Package: moat-kv-hass
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends},
  moat-kv (>= 0.50),
  moat-mqtt (>= 0.50),
Conflicts: disthass, distkv-hass
Replaces: disthass, distkv-hass
Description: Link between Home Assistant and MoaT-KV
 Home Assistant talks via MQTT. MoaT-KV has a versatile MQTT adapter.
 .
 Thus we can store Home Assistant's entitiy configuration, plus their state,
 plus the commands Home Assisant issues to get things to change their state,
 in MoaT-KV.
